1
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:59,460
I hope the money I've saved over the years

2
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:01,940
is enough to get me to Jinzhou to find Yan'er.

3
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,520
Who?

4
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,800
Who's there?

5
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,400
Brother Li.

6
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:46,800
What happened to you?

7
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,840
Didn't you leave the city?

8
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:51,810
As soon as I left,

9
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:55,360
I ran into Huang Wansan's men.

10
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,930
Let's go.

11
00:02:57,079 --> 00:02:58,360
I'll take you to a doctor.

12
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:58,880
Come on.

13
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,280
Listen to me.

14
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:05,520
When the famine hit the outskirts years ago,

15
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:09,160
thanks to Lord Su opening the granaries,

16
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,200
my life was spared.

17
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,810
To have lived this long,

18
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,400
I've already gained enough.

19
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,400
Stop talking. I'll take you to a doctor.

20
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,079
Zhaoxue.

21
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,360
You...

22
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,960
Please don't blame your father.

23
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,300
He was a good official.

24
00:03:29,760 --> 00:03:32,400
And a good...

25
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,920
Brother Li.

26
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,520
Brother Li.

27
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:47,120
Brother Li! Wake up! Brother Li!

28
00:03:55,079 --> 00:03:56,010
Little Marquis.

29
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:58,320
Cripple Li is inside.

30
00:03:59,079 --> 00:04:03,120
And this is Gu Lihan's home.

31
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,520
He is extremely dangerous.

32
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:08,880
Hurry.

33
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:09,440
Be careful, everyone.

34
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:09,680
Move it.

35
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,210
Yes, sir.

36
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,840
You Longying Guards are certainly fast.

37
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,800
But we both arrived just in time.

38
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:27,400
Indeed.

39
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,920
I just received a tip.

40
00:04:34,159 --> 00:04:36,890
The suspect inside is connected to Huang Wansan.

41
00:04:37,440 --> 00:04:39,440
I have orders from His Majesty to investigate this case,

42
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:41,440
so naturally, I must see it through.

43
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:43,159
As for the Longying Guard,

44
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,100
interfering in a Duchayuan case,

45
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,730
isn't that overstepping your bounds?

46
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,680
Search.

47
00:04:58,840 --> 00:04:59,840
Are you all right?

48
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,440
I'm fine.

49
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:08,640
I just got home

50
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:11,840
and found a dead man in my room.

51
00:05:13,320 --> 00:05:14,440
I was terrified.

52
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,780
Look at this wound.

53
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,800
The killer was ruthless.

54
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,040
One fatal strike.

55
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:29,220
This doesn't look like a Jianghu technique.

56
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,330
It looks like the technique of a Palace Guard.

57
00:05:33,880 --> 00:05:34,740
A Palace Guard?

58
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,770
Why would a Palace Guard come here?

59
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,080
This badge...

60
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,840
I thought you were the one, Gu Lihan,

61
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:54,770
who stole it from the Beizhen Fusi.

62
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:56,920
I didn't expect

63
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,840
to find it on him.

64
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:04,680
This is grave news.

65
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,880
We must enter the Palace immediately

66
00:06:06,880 --> 00:06:08,680
and report everything to His Majesty.

67
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,480
No.

68
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,920
This doesn't warrant disturbing His Majesty late at night.

69
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:17,200
Besides, Palace Guards rotate frequently.

70
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:20,000
It's not uncommon for them to end up in the Jianghu.

71
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,120
It's dangerous here.

72
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,880
Come with me to the Duchayuan for the night.

73
00:06:30,440 --> 00:06:32,320
The Beizhen Fusi is safer.

74
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,800
I won't trouble you, my lords.

75
00:06:38,840 --> 00:06:41,120
I'll just stay at an inn.

76
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,320
Lord Fang.

77
00:07:15,320 --> 00:07:17,580
Where do you think you're going, Miss Gu?

78
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,320
Huang Wansan has been executed.

79
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:22,120
So I assume everything is settled here.

80
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,840
I plan

81
00:07:22,840 --> 00:07:24,520
to go for a walk outside the city.

82
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:26,120
Do you think you alone

83
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:29,000
can really find your sister in Jinzhou?

84
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,920
When did I ever say I was going to Jinzhou to find my sister?

85
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:36,080
My sister

86
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:37,840
is just a nameless courtesan.

87
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:40,100
What does she have to do with Jinzhou?

88
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,120
Miss Su.

89
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,840
You've got the wrong person, Lord Fang.

90
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,120
Whether I am or not,

91
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,080
we both know the truth.

92
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,320
My surname is Gu.

93
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,120
Not Su.

94
00:07:57,760 --> 00:08:00,620
The surname Su, combined with the Witchcraft Case,

95
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,080
is a recipe for disaster.

96
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:03,720
Lord Fang,

97
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,610
you aren't trying to curse me, are you?

98
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,520
It has been verified.

99
00:08:11,880 --> 00:08:14,440
Only one girl is missing from Qihong Tower.

100
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,520
And that person

101
00:08:15,920 --> 00:08:19,720
is none other than Lord Su Ziliang's youngest daughter, Su Qingyan.

102
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:22,360
Ten years ago, during the Witchcraft Case,

103
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,820
Lord Su Ziliang was ordered to investigate.

104
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,320
But he was unexpectedly dragged into it

105
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,400
and lost his life.

106
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,730
Now his youngest daughter is missing.

107
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:34,280
And the eldest, missing for ten years, has reappeared.

108
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:38,280
She must be a key suspect the Imperial Court wants to capture.

109
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,600
What exactly do you want?

110
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,040
His Majesty has appointed me Imperial Envoy

111
00:08:47,040 --> 00:08:49,200
to go to Jinzhou and investigate this case.

112
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,960
You are well-versed in the ways of the Jianghu.

113
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:54,360
I want you to help me investigate.

114
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,280
I don't quite understand.

115
00:08:57,920 --> 00:09:00,480
You have plenty of talented people under your command, Lord Fang.

116
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,200
I'm just a woman.

117
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,780
How could I possibly help you?

118
00:09:07,840 --> 00:09:08,570
Don't worry.

119
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:10,970
I will keep your identity a secret.

120
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,720
You are involved in a major case now.

121
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:17,920
Being alone in the Capital puts you in constant danger.

122
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,920
You'll be safer by my side.

123
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,440
All clues point to Jinzhou now.

124
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,480
It must be the culprits' lair.

125
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:29,320
Do you think you alone

126
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:31,120
can save your sister?

127
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:36,440
If you help me solve this case

128
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,800
and atone for your crimes,

129
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:41,040
I will find a way to remove your sister from the slave registry

130
00:09:41,040 --> 00:09:42,600
and restore her freedom.

131
00:09:42,920 --> 00:09:43,960
Do you mean that?

132
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,200
Yes.

133
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,120
Alright, I agree.

134
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,090
I'll go to Jinzhou with you.

135
00:09:52,680 --> 00:09:53,940
Where are we going now?

136
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:58,120
Before we leave, I must bid farewell to my teacher.

137
00:10:09,880 --> 00:10:13,760
I don't think you need to rush to Jinzhou.

138
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,680
Didn't we discuss last night

139
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:22,200
that the Witchcraft Case might be related to the Su family?

140
00:10:22,920 --> 00:10:28,120
Why not start with the missing Su Qingyan?

141
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:33,360
You have a history with Su Ziliang.

142
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:37,800
You must not let that affect your investigation.

143
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:41,530
Rest assured, Teacher. I will handle the case impartially.

144
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,200
Good.

145
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:58,520
Teacher, we will prepare to depart for Jinzhou then.

146
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,520
Ruilang.

147
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:06,000
You're just in time. Accompany your cousin to Jinzhou.

148
00:11:06,680 --> 00:11:07,600
I'm not going.

149
00:11:07,920 --> 00:11:08,680
What?

150
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:13,480
The Dragon Shadow Guard found the clues first.

151
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:15,560
Why does Fang Ji get to be the Imperial Envoy?

152
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,320
I haven't seen you solve any cases,

153
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:20,180
but you've certainly done plenty of backstabbing.

154
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,440
Insolent!

155
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:25,880
Fang Ji is the Imperial Envoy I strongly recommended.

156
00:11:26,280 --> 00:11:27,720
He is reliable,

157
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:29,970
and deeply favored by the Emperor.

158
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:33,920
Ruilang, on this point,

159
00:11:34,320 --> 00:11:37,960
you must learn from your cousin.

160
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:46,680
You and Miss Gu have average martial arts skills.

161
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:50,290
Although Ruilang can't compare to you in other ways,

162
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:53,240
his martial arts skills are extraordinary.

163
00:11:53,800 --> 00:11:57,040
He can ensure your safety.

164
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,600
Is she going too?

165
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:02,260
Then I'm going too.

166
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:04,540
A man and a woman all alone.

167
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:07,440
Who knows what Fang Ji is up to?

168
00:12:08,040 --> 00:12:10,320
Ruilang, how can you be so dirty-minded?

169
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,680
Aiya aiheiyo.

170
00:12:22,280 --> 00:12:24,680
Ruilang, you didn't bring any attendants?

171
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:26,600
And are traveling light with us.

172
00:12:26,840 --> 00:12:28,240
That must be hard for you.

173
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:32,560
I reach out and touch...

174
00:12:32,560 --> 00:12:36,720
the eldest sister's hair.

175
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:43,360
Evil spirit!

176
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:46,000
It must be an evil spirit!

177
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,480
It must be an evil spirit!

178
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:50,760
What's going on?

179
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:52,440
I shouldn't have pushed my luck,

180
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,880
coming out at night to earn this life-threatening money.

181
00:12:54,880 --> 00:12:56,480
What are you wailing about in the middle of the night?

182
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,920
There are no evil spirits.

183
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,720
Explain clearly what happened.

184
00:13:00,960 --> 00:13:03,720
It's been very strange around here lately.

185
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,810
We are haunted by evil spirits.

186
00:13:07,600 --> 00:13:11,240
People and livestock often die suddenly at night.

187
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:14,080
They say evil spirits are claiming lives.

188
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:19,040
By the way, everyone says the Emperor has lost his virtue.

189
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,680
Nonsense.

190
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:25,040
Anyone who dares to spread rumors about His Majesty should be skinned alive.

191
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:25,840
Ruilang.

192
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:28,680
Ignorant.

193
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,960
Let's find a place to stay quickly.

194
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:33,360
It's late at night.

195
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:35,920
We'll freeze to death if we sleep outdoors.

196
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:39,480
If you can find a clean and spacious inn nearby,

197
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,840
you will be well paid.

198
00:13:40,880 --> 00:13:42,640
That's easy.

199
00:13:42,680 --> 00:13:44,840
There is an inn nearby.

200
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,840
I guarantee it's clean and spacious.

201
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:47,640
Let's go.

202
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,680
Alright.

203
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:52,120
Sit tight.

204
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,760
Hyah!

205
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:56,200
Go!

206
00:13:58,320 --> 00:13:59,720
Here we are.

207
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:02,760
This inn is a bit too shabby.

208
00:14:02,880 --> 00:14:04,360
The wind and sand are strong here.

209
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:06,720
It looks a bit old from the outside,

210
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,770
but I guarantee it's clean inside.

211
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:12,090
Besides, this is the only place to stay outside the city.

212
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,920
It's better than sleeping in the wild.

213
00:14:15,920 --> 00:14:18,440
And it looks like it's going to rain soon.

214
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,080
This will do.

215
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,240
Okay, I'll go in and tell the owner.

216
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,160
Wait.

217
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,240
What is this?

218
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,920
Anti-poison powder.

219
00:14:37,920 --> 00:14:38,840
Sprinkle it on your clothes.

220
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,900
It keeps bugs, snakes, and rats away.

221
00:14:41,560 --> 00:14:44,120
Also, the situation here is unclear.

222
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,880
We should be cautious.

223
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,760
I won't thank you.

224
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,440
The Little Marquis's words...

225
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,880
you have to take them the opposite way.

226
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:55,480
Let's go.
